        "TileImage": "$($repository 80527cca-f2bc-4bbc-8a3f-6e186d52504a).Image",
        "Description": "December 12, 1993\r\rHello there, 47\r\rToday you are back on the playing field to eliminate three targets.\r\rCEO, Philip Von Zell of Von Zell Oil Company in Munich, Germany, an oil magnate who has a taste for Moroccan girls that buys from Peter van Valdhorn.\r\rCEO, Peter van Valdhorn of Van Valdhorn International, an human trafficker of Moroccan girls.\r\rAnd last, Edward Stark of Stark Global, a gunrunner, and a human trafficker of French girls.\r\rEliminate all three without killing any civilians.",
